Package: cranscan
Title: Scans CRAN to Find Relevant R Packages
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Nicholas", "Tierney", email = "nicholas.tierney@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: cranscan provides functions to explore packages on CRAN so that you
    can more easily find related ones. It enables this through the use of a 
    shiny app similar to the package papr, which uses swiping to allow users to
    choose R packages that are related or not to their keywords.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: dplyr,
    cranlogs
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
